criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  18 years old or more;

          -  good general healthy;

          -  molars or premolar requiring endodontic treatment;

          -  at least 20 teeth;

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  root fracture;

          -  injury involving the furcation region

          -  need to behave as a prosthetic abutment;

          -  mobility greater than degree I;
